Package io.mosip.registration.dao

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AppAuthenticationDAO
    This class is used to fetch the authentication related information from the AppAuthenticationMethod.
    AppAuthenticationDetails
    This class is used to fetch only selected (process names and auth method code) columns from the AppAuthenticationMethod table.
    AppAuthenticationDetails.AppAuthentication
    This class defines the columns which are needed to be selected and fetched from the AppAuthenticationMethod.
    AppRolePriorityDetails
    This class is used to fetch only selected (role code and priority) columns from the AppRolePriority table.
    AppRolePriorityDetails.AppRolePriority
    This class defines the columns which are needed to be selected and fetched from the AppRolePriority.
    AuditDAO
    This class is used to fetch/delete audit related information to Audit table.
    AuditLogControlDAO
    This class is used to control all the operations on the AuditLogControl.
    DocumentCategoryDAO
    This class is used to fetch all the Document category related data.
    DocumentTypeDAO
    This class is used to fetch all the Document type related details.
    GenderDAO
    This class is used to fetch the gender details from Gender table.
    GlobalParamDAO
    This class is used to fetch/save/update the Global Parameter.
    GlobalParamName
    This class is used to fetch only specified columns from GlobalParam table
    LocationDAO
    This class is used to fetch all the locations present in the Location table.
    MachineMappingDAO
    This class is used to update the mapping of users and devices to the Registration Center Machine
    MasterSyncDao
    The Interface MasterSyncDao.
    PolicySyncDAO
    DAO class for PolicySync
    PreRegistrationDataSyncDAO
    This class is used to fetch the specific pre registration by passing pre registration id as parameter, To save the new pre registration record to PreRegistrationList table.
    RegistrationCenterDAO
    This class is used to get the Registration Center details from RegistrationCenter table by passing center id and language code as parameters.
    RegistrationDAO
    This class will be used to fetch/Add/Update details from the Registration and RegistrationTransaction while creating a registration packet the respective packet data will be stored tables.
    RegPacketStatusDAO
    DAO class for Repository
    ScreenAuthorizationDAO
    DAO class for RegistrationScreenAuthorization
    ScreenAuthorizationDetails
    Interface for RegistrationScreenAuthorization
    ScreenAuthorizationDetails.ScreenAuthorization
    To fetch only selected columns from table
    SyncJobConfigDAO
    DAO class for batch job configuration
    SyncJobControlDAO
    DAO class for SyncJobDAO.
    SyncTransactionDAO
    To save and update batch process
    TemplateDao
    This class is used to fetch the list of templates from Template table by passing template type code as parameter, fetch the list of templates types from TemplateType table by passing code and language code as parametrs and to fetch the list of template file formats from TemplateFileFormat table.
    UserDetailDAO
    This class is used to get respective user details by providing their id from UserDetail table.
    UserOnboardDAO
    This class is used to save the biometric details of the registration officer.
    ValidDocumentDAO
    This class is used to fetch all the ValidDocument from ValidDocument table.
